{"ja377:0.1":"Jataka ","ja377:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","ja377:0.3":"Avariyavagga ","ja377:0.4":"2. Setaketujataka ","ja377:1.1":"“Ma tata kujjhi na hi sadhu kodho, ","ja377:1.2":"Bahumpi te aditthamassutanca; ","ja377:1.3":"Mata pita disata setaketu, ","ja377:1.4":"Acariyamahu disatam pasattha. ","ja377:2.1":"Agarino annadapanavatthada, ","ja377:2.2":"Avhayika tampi disam vadanti; ","ja377:2.3":"Esa disa parama setaketu, ","ja377:2.4":"Yam patva dukkhi sukhino bhavanti”. ","ja377:3.1":"“Kharajina jatila pankadanta, ","ja377:3.2":"Dummakkharupa yeme jappanti mante; ","ja377:3.3":"Kacci nu te manusake payoge, ","ja377:3.4":"Idam vidu parimutta apaya”. ","ja377:4.1":"“Papani kammani katvana raja, ","ja377:4.2":"Bahussuto ce na careyya dhammam; ","ja377:4.3":"Sahassavedopi na tam paticca, ","ja377:4.4":"Dukkha pamucce caranam apatva”. ","ja377:5.1":"“Sahassavedopi na tam paticca, ","ja377:5.2":"Dukkha pamucce caranam apatva; ","ja377:5.3":"Mannami veda aphala bhavanti, ","ja377:5.4":"Sasamyamam caranameva saccam”. ","ja377:6.1":"“Na heva veda aphala bhavanti, ","ja377:6.2":"Sasamyamam caranameva saccam; ","ja377:6.3":"Kittinhi pappoti adhicca vede, ","ja377:6.4":"Santim puneti caranena danto”ti. ","ja377:7.1":"Setaketujatakam dutiyam. "}